{"tid":333362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"窮 到底有咩問題?","createTime":"2017-07-23T17:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T19:09:22.000Z","uid":113099,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c8267dffd5a463ee4f8f9d970abe24223010303e","tid":333362,"uid":113099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:35:09.000Z","msg":"上左連登一排 可以歸納啲見解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-喺部分人眼中 有錢人節儉就係美德 窮人慳錢就係窮酸<br />\n<br />\n-仇富既同時都睇唔起窮人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你班垃圾我唔知有幾多係自卑有幾多真係有錢 但我淨係知笑人窮既一定係無家教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1244ac87a3bc29eba67003d79add60aebaae98","tid":333362,"uid":20033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:38:58.000Z","msg":"窮人唔好笑 好笑嘅係窮人無錢扮有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過最後勸你上連登 勿認真"},{"pid":"ddeb5b647beda7d98eafad4f67146fbf94542285","tid":333362,"uid":113099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:41:10.000Z","msg":"打漏左啲:<br />\n<br />\n呢到既人真係自大到一個點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望呢班人喺現實世界都可以keep住呢份傲氣唔好畏首畏尾 因為我最睇唔起個啲揀人恰既垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f1b9e692043479d69d8f8bed91b8721a9b4152","tid":333362,"uid":26711,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:41:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上左連登一排 可以歸納啲見解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-喺部分人眼中 有錢人節儉就係美德 窮人慳錢就係窮酸<br />\n<br />\n-仇富既同時都睇唔起窮人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你班垃圾我唔知有幾多係自卑有幾多真係有錢 但我淨係知<span style=\"color: red;\">笑人窮既一定係無家教</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048e14ebe9f12c6b5c804194cb4975f596a60093","tid":333362,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:42:17.000Z","msg":"窮係冇問題 <br />\n不過係香港窮就好大問題<br />\n因為香港做咩都講錢<br />\n你唔會搵到出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b7997f68b4b78021e88860d1e14557a235d9c5","tid":333362,"uid":113099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:42:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮人唔好笑 好笑嘅係窮人無錢扮有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過最後勸你上連登 勿認真</blockquote><br />\n所以有時自卑都好可怕 但我覺得呢啲主因都係香港既價值觀出曬事"},{"pid":"c69f6da915cdc9e743b29bacfe46a9e3cc498e2e","tid":333362,"uid":113099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:46:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮係冇問題 <br />\n不過係香港窮就好大問題<br />\n因為香港做咩都講錢<br />\n你唔會搵到出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我認同窮於生存而言係有問題 學yip man套戲話濟 唔應該有貴賤之別"},{"pid":"43acaabb53ad82920254508c83da9e3855cecb06","tid":333362,"uid":60790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:53:29.000Z","msg":"社會係咁現實 尤其係香港"},{"pid":"a83a722a8d9907bef5b50959ab313c2393c63456","tid":333362,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:55:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮人唔好笑 好笑嘅係窮人無錢扮有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過最後勸你上連登 勿認真</blockquote><br />\n樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係以為咁多窮人？<br />\n你出街睇下個個揸iphone你就知香港其實唔係想像中吹到咁多窮人"},{"pid":"86b15cf227e41baba02ade4c230e2d99068d6b31","tid":333362,"uid":113099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:59:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>社會係咁現實 尤其係香港</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明雖然我只係二十出頭...但我信如果要變的話一定要由自己做起  我只係想大家發現除左錢重有好多好美好既野值得我地停低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地應該踏實但不必現實"},{"pid":"6349c1c33f401e48fa2f4d052254716d81e67dd0","tid":333362,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:01:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>窮人唔好笑 好笑嘅係窮人無錢扮有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過最後勸你上連登 勿認真</blockquote><br />\n樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係以為咁多窮人？<br />\n你出街睇下個個揸iphone你就知香港其實唔係想像中吹到咁多窮人</blockquote><br />\n揸靚車就話啫 揸住部幾千既iphone代表到乜?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fee6ca7b613f6dc79272dd3fb1863cb502f3e2c","tid":333362,"uid":113099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:06:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>窮人唔好笑 好笑嘅係窮人無錢扮有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過最後勸你上連登 勿認真</blockquote><br />\n樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係以為咁多窮人？<br />\n你出街睇下個個揸iphone你就知香港其實唔係想像中吹到咁多窮人</blockquote><br />\n....um我個人認為窮呢樣係相對 香港個堅尼系數真係出曬事 <br />\n<br />\n但只要你細心留意下日常真係唔難發現低下階層既生活係幾慘..有時慘到我真係覺得唔應該發生喺一個咁大既城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64fcb28a4cbc80c92c9d7718c9f87503b76873d","tid":333362,"uid":15711,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:07:03.000Z","msg":"好多連燈仔自己窮，但又眼紅人勤力，將人地勤力標籤成奴！想其他人陪佢窮一世！"},{"pid":"82f37f1f155605e9650f915ec06203c341c20c37","tid":333362,"uid":113099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:11:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多連燈仔自己窮，但又眼紅人勤力，將人地勤力標籤成奴！想其他人陪佢窮一世！</blockquote><br />\n認同 難聽啲講 不思進取唔正視問題 同時好多見咩都踩左先 <br />\n<br />\n自己好彩叫有機會見識下西方文化 唔係祟洋同先別論佢地係唔係發自真心 但佢地講野等等都係偏正面 而唔似香港人咁mean"},{"pid":"ee87f703f0672e1f0bc6d31b4212f3faee65fe8c","tid":333362,"uid":54223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:30:25.000Z","msg":"窮= 原罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d0bbb4901fd4674be10437cef942ba6ab3c169","tid":333362,"uid":113099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T19:09:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮= 原罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n希望有有生之年可以見到社會風氣轉變"}]}